        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: project visible session transcripts",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nVisible WhatsApp/group session surfaces were showing internal delivery artifacts as if they were user-visible chat history. On `agent:alfred:whatsapp:group:120363425559039020@g.us`, `sessions_history(includeTools=false)` exposed assistant tool-call-only rows and terminal source-delivery confirmations like `Sent the Branch Basics links in WhatsApp.` `sessions_list(includeLastMessage=true)` also used those confirmations as previews.\n\nThis PR keeps raw transcript records intact for replay/debugging and `includeTools=true`, while projecting a cleaner visible chat transcript for history/list/preview surfaces.\n\n## Summary\n\n- Add shared visible-chat transcript projection helpers.\n- Hide tool-call/tool-result artifacts and terminal source-delivery confirmations from visible WA/group history and previews.\n- De-duplicate `delivery-mirror` assistant rows only when the same bounded projected window contains the synthetic `openclawMessageToolMirror` replacement.\n- Preserve standalone `delivery-mirror` assistant rows so bounded history/list/preview windows do not lose the only delivered reply.\n- Preserve raw transcript records and `includeTools=true`/debug paths.\n\n## Redacted Behavior Proof\n\nFull-context message-tool turn:\n\n- Before visible projection: redacted user request, raw `provider=openclaw/model=delivery-mirror` delivered text, assistant `message` tool call, tool result, terminal `Sent ... in WhatsApp.` confirmation.\n- After visible projection: redacted user request plus one synthetic `openclawMessageToolMirror` assistant row with the delivered text. Raw tool artifacts and terminal confirmation are hidden from visible chat; raw records remain available with `includeTools=true`.\n\nBounded-window standalone delivery mirror:\n\n- Before this review fix: a window containing only a redacted user request plus `provider=openclaw/model=delivery-mirror` delivered text projected to the user request only, so `sessions_history`, hydrated `sessions_list` messages, and `lastMessagePreview` lost the delivered reply.\n- After this review fix: the same bounded window preserves the standalone delivery mirror. The delivered text remains visible in `sessions_history(includeTools=false)`, `sessions_list(messageLimit=...)`, and last-message preview.\n\n## Evidence\n\nLocal verification on branch `fix/koro-whatsapp-message-tool-final` at `baf4165989`:\n\n- `node scripts/test-projects.mjs src/agents/tools/sessions-history-tool.test.ts src/agents/tools/sessions-list-tool.test.ts src/gateway/session-utils.fs.test.ts` passed: gateway shard 4 files / 376 tests; agents shard 2 files / 20 tests.\n- `node scripts/test-projects.mjs src/agents/openclaw-tools.sessions.test.ts src/agents/tools/sessions-history-tool.test.ts src/agents/tools/sessions-list-tool.test.ts src/gateway/session-utils.fs.test.ts src/gateway/server.chat.gateway-server-chat.test.ts src/auto-reply/reply/dispatch-from-config.reply-dispatch.test.ts src/auto-reply/reply/dispatch-from-config.test.ts` passed: gateway shard 6 files / 448 tests; auto-reply shard 2 files / 225 tests; agents shard 3 files / 55 tests.\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.test.src.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/test-src.tsbuildinfo` exited clean.\n- `git diff --check` exited clean.\n\n## MC\n\n- Implements MC task `js7chanc5ewxg2jwf6aqwbmdt989g9fj`.\n- Keep MC open until this PR is merged to `origin/main` and verified there.",
